des:
Get unofficial to-the-minute stats & fun facts on the Packers by Fresh Digital Group. This skill isn’t sponsored or endorsed by the Packers.

Here’s some ways you can use the skill. We have given you many different ways for you to talk to Alexa:



General Updates:


Alexa, ask Packers Fan how are the Packers doing? 

Alexa, ask Packers Fan who do the Packers play next?

Alexa, ask Packers Fan Aaron Rodgers (or any player's First name, Last name) touchdown update. 



Fun Facts about the Packers:


Alexa, ask Packers Fan to tell me some trivia about the Packers. 

Alexa, ask Packers Fan how many Super Bowls have the Packers won?
